::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe opens his eyes, raising his head. His whole body hurt as he 
moved. He looks up, seeing a translucent glowing screen in front of him. 
Turning his head, he sees that he is surrounded by such screens, forming a 
cube prison. He growls.

"Cloak."

Once again, DeathScythe seemingly disapears. He reaches into his storage 
compartment, looking for a certain object.
